{"tid":815724,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"岩岩聽到個港女話要食大雞巴","createTime":"2018-09-12T09:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-12T12:10:20.000Z","uid":5572,"like":34,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"502e1a2237f27b7957173ee1f1b89a34ebec351e","tid":815724,"uid":5572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:07:39.000Z","msg":"話說 我係台灣士林夜市行緊 見到豪大大諗住買塊食下所以去左排隊，聽到前面有2條港女同個店員講 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 港女 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 店員<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 請給我一份雞巴（全場人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 對不起，你要什麼？<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我要一份大雞巴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不好意思我們沒有<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 怎麼可能沒有，指住個menu話我要這個大雞巴<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 啊一份&rsquo;雞排&lsquo;對吧 <br />\n<br />\n最後條港女走緊仲問佢朋友雞巴咩意思 我全程笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029634e4b29e363a70fe950253b2b4247e7618ce","tid":815724,"uid":5572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:12:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0231505a6b15c8113fe28ee65f782cb9a5b44009","tid":815724,"uid":54502,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"今次好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fac6a058f1083891d06b12e48bf10a4beba56e61","tid":815724,"uid":64632,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T09:15:32.000Z","msg":"冇是咁的 0分"},{"pid":"80ef4e07bba64a0c0f107cd5c14d7f1b00321d2e","tid":815724,"uid":165196,"like":1,"dislike":5,"scor